[[File:Xeno_furniture.jpg|thumb|280px|The Xeno furniture line]]
'''Xeno''' was the name of a furniture line designed and manufactured by the [[Affodies Crafthouse of Pure Neimoidia]]. The line included a couch, a recliner, a table, a desk, a desk lamp and a [[Carpet/Legends|rug]].

In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]] [[Jag Silon]] gave out pieces of this furniture line to members of the [[Galactic Vacant Building Demolishing Movement]].

==Behind the scenes==
These pieces of furniture were rewards for players of ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'' that participated in the house packup events in [[2007]] and [[2009]].

